<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM12.4">
<l>aṅkait talattiṭai yāḻikoṇṭā ṉavaṉmukat taṉṟi viḻiyēṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>ceṅkaccuk koṇṭukaṇ ṇāṭaiyārttuc ciṟumā ṉiṭavaraik kāṇilnāṇuṅ</l>
<l>koṅkait talamivai nōkkikkāṇīr kōvinta ṉukkallāl vāyilpōkā</l>
<l>iṅkuttai vāḻvai yoḻiyavēpōy yamuṉaik karaikkeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look carefully at these breasts that are ashamed when seeing petty humans,</l>
<l>shielding [their] eyes with  fine corset-garment, saying, ‘I shall not look at</l>
<l>anything but the face of He who held a discus in [His] palm!’</l>
<l>They shall not enter an entrance other than Govinda’s!</l>
<l>[So,] send me to the banks of Yamunā</l>
<l rend="indent">Going [there] so that life here ends!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
